txt.en: Defeat the Matron of the Fang
Your mission is to kill spiders in Ushbarab and slay the Matron of the Fang when she emerges to defend her nest.
Defeated the Matron of the Fang
Find and defeat the Matron of the Fang in Ushbarab.
The Matron of the Fang emerges to defend her nest!
A scout has arrived to escort you back to Ub Nishir
To the north-west of Maur√ªsh the spiders grow more foetid and strong. There is a call from the coalition at Ub Nishir to cull the matron at the head of the nest.
'Greetings! You did well to slay the matron. Come, let's return to Ub Nishir.'
